<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹lh ạlḥb njạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹lh ạlḥb njạny .. bmwt ạlṣlb ạ̉ḥyạny
 (brwḥ ạlqds yhdyny .. yʿzyny wyrʿạny)2
 1- fhl yạ qwm mn ḥbiⁿ .. nẓyr dẖlk ạlḥb
 (brgẖm ạlsẖr wạlbʿd .. lạ̉jly mạt bạlṣlb)2
 2- gẖdạ mạḍy mstwraⁿạ .. wṣạr ạlạ̹tẖm mgẖfwraⁿạ
 (wfạḍ ạlqlb tsbyḥaⁿạ .. wthlylaⁿạ wtqdyraⁿạ)2
 3- tʿạlwạ wạsẖhdwạ ạlḥb .. wdẖwqwạ wạnẓrwạ ạlrb
 (ạ̹ly̱ ạlḥyạẗ ydʿwkm .. flbwạ wạftḥwạ ạlqlb)2</lyrics>
